{"tid":1702242,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大三罷到底大家有幾大決心？做好強制全港大罷工的心理準備未？","createTime":"2019-11-09T14:55:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T09:47:13.000Z","uid":23991,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"e16450320a4d0c585d2c5358c3596489fb1bf625","tid":1702242,"uid":23991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T14:55:03.000Z","msg":"今次唔係大家第一次搞罷工<br />\n上幾次好多人第二日就如常返工<br />\n<br />\n大家係咪真做好左停擺公司<br />\n停擺全港的心理準備？<br />\n如果係的，我求大家每人諗多一步可以點做<br />\n<br />\n同一時間，當日決定照常返工的你<br />\n記得要諗下係當日混亂的情況下點保障自己<br />\n以下係幾點建議  大家屌得細力D<br />\n<br />\n1. 你公司有冇任何野係壞左就運作唔到？<br />\n有冇任何account/server/硬件設備係會壞左就用唔到？<br />\n如果有，大家就算返到公司 <span style=\"color: red;\">都記得double check下</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記得<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\">小心唔好</span></span>搞壞重要的設備</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2.交通 - 大家講左超合作運動好耐<br />\n除左乖乖地坐車<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">記得</span></span>要check下設備有冇爛<br />\n唔好多手去<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">亂搞D設施</span></span><br />\n車箱有任何可疑物品（例如好似之前懷疑爆炸品個D吉箱）<br />\n一定要搵專業人仕處理<br />\n同要小心任何有機會<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">損壞車箱/路軌/高速路面</span></span>的行為<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 任何人多聚集的地方就好有機會有堆曱甴警係到開槍<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">強烈要求罷工的人</span><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><strong><span style=\"color: navy;\">唔好</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">聚集係商業區<br />\n搞到塞車/D人要提早收工收市<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: navy;\">咁就仆街啦</span></span> </span></span> <br />\n作為大愛的香港人 最怕就係示威影響到人<br />\n搞到人被逼罷工 就唔好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">覺得有用可唔可以幫手推下同實行</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"5a66a095516f54874ba70b51b0267ddec24d3c93","tid":1702242,"uid":23991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T14:58:23.000Z","msg":"幫自己推下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c723c87f1ccfbbf47c9a454ad34200850a6c2d8c","tid":1702242,"uid":125168,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T14:58:38.000Z","msg":"順便係到宣傳gay巴嘅工會計劃：<br />\n<br />\n🔴二百萬三罷聯合陣線🔴<br />\n抗爭 | 工會 | 罷工 | 行業行動<br />\n頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/hkonstrike\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkonstrike&d=NEeHCsu%2FqEZuPycg%2B0xSpgUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=22968d7e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkonstrike</a><br />\nGroup List <a href=\"https://t.me/hkonstrike/186\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkonstrike%2F186&d=NEeHCsu%2FqEZuPycg%2B0xSpgUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=0d5da03d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkonstrike/186</a><br />\nFB <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2JQLM2f\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2JQLM2f&d=NEeHCsu%2FqEZuPycg%2B0xSpgUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=07262e2e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2JQLM2f</a><br />\nIG <a href=\"https://bit.ly/33hmGRR\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F33hmGRR&d=NEeHCsu%2FqEZuPycg%2B0xSpgUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=58a9feb4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/33hmGRR</a>"},{"pid":"ac5772166bfbf151e77dc6a684c2e6300cb80df7","tid":1702242,"uid":23991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T14:58:47.000Z","msg":"好撚唔想返工呀 屌你老母！！！！！！！！！！！"},{"pid":"52fd2a9d5bbe520fedfd99723e6205976721d2a1","tid":1702242,"uid":23991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c723c87f1ccfbbf47c9a454ad34200850a6c2d8c","tid":1702242,"uid":125168,"like":3,"dis